---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About | The Jeff Crilley Show">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 sm:py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">About Jeff Crilley</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-gray max-w-none">
      <p>Jeff Crilley is a veteran journalist, Emmy Award-winning reporter, and media expert who has spent decades telling the stories that matter. Now, through The Jeff Crilley Show, he brings those same storytelling skills to long-form conversations with fascinating people from every walk of life.</p>
      <p>From business leaders to entertainers, innovators to community champions, every episode is a deep dive into what makes extraordinary people tick.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
